      "    (Ch06 — brew before entering)",
      "  └ Slow Falling: critical for End descent (Ch13)",
      "  └ Splash/Lingering: throw at enemies or allies",
      "  └ Arrows of X: combine lingering with arrows",
      "",
      "◈ THIRST INTERACTION",
      "  └ Drinking potions counts as hydration",
      "  └ Water bottles fill ThirstWasTaken bar",
      "  └ Awkward potions: neutral (slight hydration)",
      "  └ Effect potions: small hydration bonus",
      "  └ Nether survival: Fire Resistance + hydration potions",
